t and pepper and mix with aid of spatula. Cook <b>12 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>, placing simmering basket instead of measuring cup onto mixing bowl lid."},{"content":"Add pancetta and reserved spinach mixture, stir with aid of spatula and cook <b>2 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>, placing simmering basket instead of measuring cup onto mixing bowl lid."},{"content":"Transfer into thermal serving bowl or other large bowl. Place a bowl onto mixing bowl lid and weigh peas and butter into it. Transfer into thermal serving bowl or other large bowl then add reserved Parmesan mixture. Stir to combine. Cover and allow to rest for 1 minute, then transfer into serving bowls and garnish with extra basil before serving."}],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","45m","4 portions"]}